# Case Study: SaaS Migration for Recruitment Platform

## 🏢 Client
Confidential Recruitment Company

## 📅 Duration
2021

## 🎯 Objective
Migrate legacy on-premise recruitment application to Azure SaaS, automate billing and payroll integrations.

## 🧩 Solution
- Migrated platform to Azure with full DevOps support
- Created automated data extracts and REST APIs
- Streamlined architecture for payroll feeds and reporting

## 🛠️ Technologies
Azure, Boomi, REST APIs, DevOps Pipelines, SQL Server

## 📈 Impact
- £150k–£200k in annual headcount savings
- Improved data feed reliability and audit transparency
